    <li><strong>Don't reuse passwords</strong> from other accounts</li>
    <li><strong>Consider using a password manager</strong> for better security</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div style="background-color: #f0f9ff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9; margin: 30px 0;">
